snippet.title: Black One Blood Brothers - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1621560/Black_One_Blood_Brothers/

Black One Blood Brothers is a single-player tactical FPS where planning and coordination determine mission success. Take command of an elite squad, customize your operators to adapt to any situation, and complete 20 high-risk missions in a dynamic campaign.
